sub_title: Aerospace & Defense Industry Marketing Coordinator for Simcenter | Siemens Digital Industries Software
summary:
As a marketing Master 2 student and an accomplished traveler, my desire to learn and open-mindedness make me able to adapt quickly to different environments and ready to develop my skills.

After several internships and four years as a business student, my skills and motivations have surfaced. I am human-oriented, a team worker and implicated in my given tasks. Having traveled to various places for my studies, my love for learning languages has grown. I am currently learning Spanish and Korean in my free time.
